{"tid":1023501,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"近5個賽季英超TOP6轉會net spend","createTime":"2019-02-15T20:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T07:13:44.000Z","uid":3640,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3ddabcac10f3e9f15307dafb4286b6db9d66251e","tid":1023501,"uid":3640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T20:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/02/16/FxviY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F02%2F16%2FFxviY3.png&h=6362bdef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: transfermarkt<br />\n<br />\n1. 曼城<br />\n2. 曼聯<br />\n3. 阿仙奴<br />\n4. 車路士<br />\n5. 利物浦<br />\n6. 熱刺<br />\n<br />\n頭兩隊大家都估到 冇咩特別<br />\n只係反映到曼城轉會質素比較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最估唔到阿記原來都洗唔少 仲多過車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返net spend 最高個年16/17<br />\n沙卡同Mustafi分別成40m同35m左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實阿記唔係真係窮到仆街 似係買人柒柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見阿迷屌冇錢所以真係估你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利記柒完14/15 (Lovren, Markovic, Balotelli, Moreno)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同15/16 (Benteke) 之後換高普估唔到頭2季都賺錢 (當然多謝coutinho)<br />\n係上年好似有d料到先放水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車仔一路俾人印象都係大洗既就估唔到洗少過阿記<br />\n西女人好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱刺就冇野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6871706071739b9efc5678394d3fae0c9202a5b5","tid":1023501,"uid":3640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T20:46:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/premier-league/fuenfjahresvergleich/wettbewerb/GB1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/